&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt; The Kenjya-Trusant Group is looking for a Master Scheduler responsible for developing, maintaining, and optimizing integrated project schedules to support the successful execution and timely delivery of program objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Job Functions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
