&lt;li&gt;Ensure all scheduling activities comply with company policies, contractual requirements, and industry standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and up-to-date documentation of schedules and related communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance and support to junior schedulers and project team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and train team members on scheduling best practices and tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
